OL,3,CImages showcase what new Premier Inn
OL,4,Cfor Carlisle could look like
OL,6,FNew images have been released
OL,7,Fshowcasing the possible transformation
OL,8,Fof the former Central Plaza Hotel site
OL,9,Fin Carlisle city centre.
OL,11,FPlanning documents have been submitted
OL,12,Fby Whitbread PLC to Cumberland Council
OL,13,Fover plans to create a new 104-bedroom
OL,14,FPremier Inn hotel.
OL,16,FThe development is set to see
OL,17,Finvestment of up to #12 million and 25
OL,18,Fjobs created on Victoria Viaduct after
OL,19,FWhitbread PLC acquired the site
OL,20,Fearlier this year.
