OL,4,Cfor Carlisle could look like
OL,6,FJill Anderson, Acquisition Manager for
OL,7,FWhitbread in the north of England,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Since announcing our plans in
OL,9,FMay 2025 people have told us that they
OL,10,Fwish to see the vacant Central Plaza
OL,11,Fsite brought back into long-term use.
OL,13,F"They also welcome the new employment
OL,14,Fopportunities and positive economic
OL,15,Fbenefits the hotel will bring to the
OL,16,Fcity. We're very grateful for all the
OL,17,Fsupport we've received so far from
OL,18,Fstakeholders and representative groups
OL,19,Fwe have spoken to.
