OL,3,CImages showcase what new Premier Inn
OL,4,Cfor Carlisle could look like
OL,6,F"The site on West Walls is not an easy
OL,7,Flocation to redevelop into a hotel and
OL,8,Fwe've had to be flexible to create a
OL,9,Fdesign that meets our operational
OL,10,Frequirements and is economically
OL,11,Fviable.
OL,13,F"The contemporary design we are
OL,14,Fproposing responds positively to the
OL,15,Fhistoric context and will create an
OL,16,Factive frontage onto both Victoria
OL,17,FViaduct and West Walls. We're eager to
OL,18,Fmove the proposal forward, get onto
OL,19,Fsite and deliver the package of
OL,20,Fbenefits the hotel will create."
