OL,3,CImages showcase what new Premier Inn
OL,4,Cfor Carlisle could look like
OL,6,FPlans have been submitted to create a
OL,7,Ffive-storey Premier Inn with up to
OL,8,F30,000 guests expected to stay at the
OL,9,Fhotel, Whitbread PLC say.
OL,11,FIn a statement the company said:
OL,12,F"These customers are anticipated to
OL,13,Fspend more than #4 million a year
OL,14,Fwithin the visitor economy during
OL,15,Ftheir stay according to an independent
OL,16,Feconomic impact assessment submitted
OL,17,Fas part of the planning application,
OL,18,Fsupporting the leisure and tourism
OL,19,Fsector in the region.
