OL,3,CImages showcase what new Premier Inn
OL,4,Cfor Carlisle could look like
OL,6,F"Around 25 new permanent hospitality
OL,7,Fjobs are also anticipated to be
OL,8,Fcreated on opening with around 45
OL,9,Festablished jobs in the construction
OL,10,Fsupply chain expected to be supported
OL,11,Fduring the #12 million build.
OL,13,F"Subject to planning, Whitbread is
OL,14,Fhoping to commence development in 2026
OL,15,Fand is targeting to welcome its first
OL,16,Fcustomers before the end of 2028.
