OL,6,F"In line with the company's
OL,7,Fsustainability policy the proposed
OL,8,Fhotel will be powered by electricity
OL,9,Fgenerated from renewable sources and
OL,10,Fthe proposed building will incorporate
OL,11,Fheat recovery systems and air source
OL,12,Fheat pumps to create a low energy
OL,13,Fdemand."
